Hi!

I can see the autograder results for pset 3 are out but it looks like the final 8 tests on my submission took longer than 4 seconds to run and so were terminated by the autograder. That portion of my code does take a while to run, but it does run to completion and passed the test cases we were given. Do the tests need to run in under 4 seconds to count for points?
subject: Pset 3 Autograder Question
